    "text": "Woe to you!"
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Muhammad Habib Shakir",
    "text": "Again (consider how) nearer to you and nearer."
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Abdullah Yusuf Ali",
    "text": "Again, Woe to thee, (O men!), yea, woe!"
  },
  {
